{"title":"Ritchey Drops BIG News About the New Outback Frame Upgrades","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-outback-frame-upgrades-xxl/","date":1742499597000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-hero-e1742497543526.webp\" width=\"1124\" height=\"576\" alt=\"(Photo / Ritchey)\" /></p>\n<p>If you take Tom Ritchey’s 50 years of bicycle crafting and design, and combine it with the fact that he still rides 10,000 miles a year (mostly off-road), you get an icon that knows a thing or two about bikes. And, the Ritchey Outback is a culmination of that experience. The Outback has become iconic in its own right in the world of gravel and adventure riding and has become possibly their best-selling model. And now you can get it in two new finishes and a new XXL size!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-first-pic-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Ritchey)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Released in 2018, the Outback has been an uncompromising force in terms of ability and popularity. These updates will elevate the user’s riding experience further. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset looking comfy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-looking-comfy-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset finishing climb\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-finishing-climb-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some other highlights for the newly updated Outback include internal routing for a dropper, new rack mounts on the fork crown, and internal dynamo routing. The Aurora and Winter Sage colors are also new.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"787\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset in the dirt\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt-297x183.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt-120x74.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-in-the-dirt-768x472.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Outback is made with Ritchey’s proprietary, heat-treated, triple-butted Logic steel tube set. It also comes equipped with an updated carbon Adventure fork with multi-purpose and fender mounts. The fork also rocks a 1-1/8″ straight steerer.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset internal dropper post\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-internal-dropper-post-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Geometry</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"898\" height=\"550\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset geo chart\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275.webp 898w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275-297x182.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275-120x73.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-geo-chart-e1742497687275-768x470.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Maybe the biggest news is the inclusion of an all-new frame size–XXL which is meant for riders 6’2″ or taller. The full size range now spans from XS to XXL, and will fit a wider range of riders than before. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Outback Retail &amp; Specs</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"753\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset winter sage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage-297x175.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage-120x71.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-winter-sage-768x452.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Winter Sage</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"739\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset aurora\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora-297x171.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora-120x69.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-aurora-768x443.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Aurora</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $1599 (frameset)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sizes available: XS / S / M / L / XL / XXL</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Heat-treated, triple-butted Ritchey Logic tubeset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>142mm spacing (12mm alloy thru-axle included)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Crankset min/max ring size – single 36 to 46t / double: 46/30t to 50/34t</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Can accommodate 1X or 2X chainrings</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bottle cage mounts: 3</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rack and Fender mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stealth wire routing for semi-wireless Di2 groupsets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>DSP internal (seat tube only) routing is available</li>\n\n\n\n<li>WCS headset included (upper IS42/28.6 – 16mm stack height | lower IS42/30)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Replaceable stainless-steel derailleur hanger</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ritchey Carbon Adventure Fork with multi-purpose rack and fender mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Flat-mount brake compatibility</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tire Clearance: 700 x 48mm or 650 x 2.0” (depending on tire/rim manufacturer)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Frame Weight: 2,175 g (L w/o thru-axle)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fork Weight: 445g (uncut w/ thru-axle)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Colors: Aurora and Winter Sage</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling.webp\" alt=\"Ritchey Updated 2025 Outback Frameset alt cycling\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Ritchey-Updated-2025-Outback-Frameset-alt-cycling-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://ritcheylogic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RitcheyLogic.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ritchey-outback-frame-upgrades-xxl/\">Ritchey Drops BIG News About the New Outback Frame Upgrades</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2ea06ce6631f65f91270be81444a498e82ff638a3348f70e0112d8b9dfc09415","category":"Cycling"}